   1232          /***************************************************************************//**
   1233           * State machine for leader mode in blocking I2C transfer.
   1234           *
   1235           * @details
   1236           *   Implements a blocking state machine for I2C leader (master) mode
   1237           *   transfers. It manages the sequence of sending the follower (slave) address,
   1238           *   handling 7-bit and 10-bit addressing, transmitting and/or receiving data,
   1239           *   and processing all relevant I2C protocol events (ACK, NACK, STOP, errors).
   1240           *   The function blocks until the transfer is complete, an error occurs, or the
