   1245           * @param[in] tx_len      Number of bytes to transmit.
   1246           * @param[out] rx_buffer  Pointer to the receive buffer (can be NULL if not receiving).
   1247           * @param[in] rx_len      Number of bytes to receive.
   1248           * @param[in] timeout     Timeout duration for the blocking transfer, in milliseconds (0 = no timeout).
   1249           *
