   1887           * @return Status code indicating the result of the operation.
   1888           *
   1889           * @note
   1890           *   - This function is ONLY for I2C leader mode operations
   1891           *   - Leader initiates communication by sending follower address
   1892           *   - DMA channel interrupts are disabled; completion handled via I2C interrupts
   1893           *
   1894           * @warning
   1895           *   - Must be called with i2c_handle->operating_mode == SL_I2C_LEADER_MODE
