   1984           * Sets up a non-blocking DMA transfer for the I2C follower device.
   1985           *
   1986           * @details
   1987           *   Configures the I2C peripheral to perform a DMA-based data transfer
   1988           *   in follower (slave) mode without blocking the CPU. Prepares the necessary DMA
   1989           *   channels and I2C settings to enable efficient data movement between the I2C bus
   1990           *   and memory.
   1991           *
